<shortdesc>Use the <keyword conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/vbnmdpt"/> verb to
    create an encrypted PIN block with the same PIN and a different PAN. The account data may
    change, but changing the PIN is to be avoided. This service creates a new encrypted PIN block
    and MAC on the encrypted PIN block that is used to accept the PAN change at an authorization
    node.</shortdesc>
