<section>
<p>You can use this service to perform the following tasks: </p>
<ul>
<li>Generate an encrypted PIN block in PBF-1 format with a changed PAN to be used at the
authorization node to create a PIN reference value.</li>
<li>Generate a CMAC over the encrypted PIN block for validation.</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section>
<note rev="sh20i1">This verb supports <keyword
conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/pcihsm2016"/> compliant-tagged key tokens.</note>
